Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:40.06,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:42.68,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:45.98,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,No wake-up kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:31.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You got her out safely, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer one of the Planetary Gears,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:43.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't think I can go inside the {\i1}Blume{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:54.39,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The Midsummer's Knights are to gather \Nin the briefing room in thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.13,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.64,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.39,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen the real thing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:09.66,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The rumors that they secretly came \Nto the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0} were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:13.38,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Jack and Commander Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:17.55,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Two of the top three Intercept \NFaction leaders are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:23.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,As you're aware, the Kiltgangs are \Nattacking more frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:27.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we in the Intercept Faction \Nintend to fight them to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:31.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But if we remain on defense forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,they'll eventually break through \Nthe Impacter defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Which would mean the Earth is doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:44.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So we are finally initiating our primary \Nplan, Operation Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, explain the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:49.20,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.58,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Nishikubo doesn't seem to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was sending someone in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Still a kid, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.93,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Daichi Manatsu, of the Midsummer's Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:10.41,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,We will destroy the Cocoon, the core of the \NPlanetary Gears' fortress carrier {\i1}Oberon{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.14,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,which orbits around Uranus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:17.90,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That is our counteroffensive plan against \Nthe Kiltgangs, Operation Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.46,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So they're the Midsummer's Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:24.26,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine, Nebula Engine, and Flare Engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:28.26,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,our three manned Impacters, will \Nbe loaded on the spaceship {\i1}Kivotos{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:32.22,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,which will dock with the {\i1}Blume{\i0}, \Ncurrently connected to the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:37.92,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Blume{\i0}'s Entangle Link Navigation \Nenables hyperspace travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:42.55,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,We'll reach orbit around Uranus a few \Nhours after the mission begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:48.74,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll use the Engine series aboard \Nthe {\i1}Kivotos{\i0} to destroy {\i1}Oberon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:52.48,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The boosted plasmagnum, \Na destructive weapon that will
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:58.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,completely delete the intelligence information \Ncontained within the Livlasters' Orgone energy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:04.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,and convert it to pure energy, will be \Nloaded onto both the Earth and Nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Alonzo has calculated that this weapon is capable
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:13.02,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,of destroying the Cocoon, which forms the \N{\i1}Oberon{\i0}'s core and holds the Ego Blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:17.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, we'll need to do a test before we attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But we can use this to wipe \Nout the Planetary Gears
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,that have invaded the Solar System.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:29.38,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I've received a report \Nthat your Livlaster's output
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:33.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,has exceeded the energy \Nrequirement for this weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:38.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But can you replicate that number?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:42.46,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:50.87,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Can they really handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nishikubo chose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.89,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I believe in him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:02.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The idea is to eliminate the \NKivotos Plan's cold sleep block.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:07.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, if the Ark Faction \Nfinds out, we'll have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.76,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,How did it feel to be back in space after so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for an old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave space to the young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:20.02,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But not just any young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The young men and women who go into space
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,must be the chosen ones, \Nwho will carry humanity's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.49,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot let the Intercept Faction \Nget any further out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:36.32,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they told the public media \Nthat the spaceship {\i1}Blume{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:39.55,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,which surfaced in the seas around Tanegashima,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:43.75,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,was a secretly developed giant \Nasteroid defense interceptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:48.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,All of this just makes it vexing that \Nwe can't tell them the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:54.06,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The Intercept Faction's leaders are \Ngathering aboard the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.10,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.18,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:06:59.90,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Pointer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.40,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Will that be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:07.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Pointer is on his way, not as a Salty Dog member,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:10.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,but on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He's perfect for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:17.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He hates them more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:20.04,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellitejack
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:29.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The inter-satellite transport ship {\i1}Nipper{\i0} \Nis now arriving from Delta-1, at Dock 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.42,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akari's coming on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:33.64,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Just as happy as I was to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.10,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she gets here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.31,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:12.73,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.61,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.15,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There was no direct shuttle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in via Delta-1 was a \Nbigger pain than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:29.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Combat training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.66,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,When I win, the Blue Star is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be that easy, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Those two boys are flirting with each other again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.14,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.56,Default - italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The contacts Salty Dog gave me worked perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.04,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:34.92,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the beloved idol Ai-chan \Nis here to be {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}'s
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.22,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,governor for a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.96,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:54.65,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Governor for a Day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.43,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Pounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.06,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Pounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.91,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.78,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are idols important?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:09.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Almost as important as magical girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:22.70,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,So today, for a special summer project,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.77,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I've been governor of the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0} for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:31.54,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Globe just stunned the world when a \Ngiant asteroid defense interceptor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.27,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,was launched from Tanegashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:39.82,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you can tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:45.20,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get something so large up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We used cutting-edge laser propulsion technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:52.13,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Laser propulsion! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:56.69,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Then, then... The stories saying that \Npeople saw a bright ray of light
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:58.84,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,shooting into the night sky in Tanegashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.95,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Could those have anything to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.81,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.95,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,This planet can't create a device like \Nthat with its present technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.27,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Puck is not the only liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.11,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Amara and his friends have moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:21.84,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They plan to do something on the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.95,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Let's see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:39.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... A lot of this involves military secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't tell you any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:46.30,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking the time to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.48,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I got a chance to visit this satellite,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:54.38,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,on the frontier of space development, \Nand to meet all of the wonderful people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.36,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,who work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.17,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.18,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you back on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.66,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.56,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ai-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.15,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Ai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.46,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.81,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Ai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.45,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But it really was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.72,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.92,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Ai-chan, for the rest of your time here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.24,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,we'll show you around the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.60,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.64,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:37.98,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,How can you win without blocking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I've been doing this longer than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.07,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do it, so can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:48.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way you never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.62,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Good job today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:58.46,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! A pool in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing special about a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.05,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is my first time visiting \Na pool outside of photo shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.77,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:10.53,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Your job doesn't allow you a lot of \Nfreedom in your private life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.68,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.14,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.45,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have many friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.89,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,When I go out, I have to worry \Nabout people watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:24.86,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully, I think I'm hard to hang out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:29.61,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But here, you don't have to \Nworry about other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:34.18,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, there aren't \Nmany boys our age around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:47.30,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,That's Daichi Manatsu-kun \Nand Teppei Arashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.82,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,They're boys our age!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.51,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ai. Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.74,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:57.87,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is my first time talking to a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:59.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's more into trends than I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:01.13,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Trends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:13.12,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And he's totally unaffected...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Both commanders seemed concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:21.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,As am I, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Akari is still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,She's an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.80,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Since she joined Globe, I've learned that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:37.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi Manatsu still looks like \Na child to me, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:42.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, we have to leave him in \Ncharge of such a major operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.14,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confident in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:52.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,When I first heard the reports about \NHana Mutou and Teppei Arashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.81,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:58.04,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why you'd allow such \Ndangerous elements on your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:02.88,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you told Hana you'd be her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If she becomes my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,she can get the rights of an Earthling \Nand a Japanese citizenship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:15.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Once the operation is over, I can give \Nher a place to come home to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.87,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you wanted to make \Nher your daughter was because,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.65,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,after meeting her, your \Nintuition told you to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:33.59,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the shot \Nbar where we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that one in Daikanyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:40.16,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't normally do things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.71,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But despite never having seen you \Nbefore, I talked to you that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:47.67,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I felt I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:54.03,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,We've split up now, but I still consider \Nmyself lucky to have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:16:00.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I think my intuition was right in telling \Nme to talk to you that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:06.91,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, I think that's the only way \Nhumans can judge what's truly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:12.78,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe in my intuition and yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:18.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Teppei Arashi is an enemy \Navatar and retains his memories as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.42,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei isn't dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:35.71,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's an indispensable member \Nof the Midsummer's Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Did you talk to them about the Planter Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.65,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing their best, but there's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:44.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:51.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But why would they send an idol as a \Ngovernor for a day at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.95,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The PR department came up with the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I took advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.37,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good feint for the real operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:05.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Ark Faction can't do anything crazy \Nwith an idol aboard? Was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:10.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We're on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:13.26,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.91,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She really is cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.43,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.83,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.42,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.93,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:06.40,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Kivotos{\i0} spaceship holds the people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.91,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,who were entrusted with humanity's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.59,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send them back to Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:16.57,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,and use the spaceship they were going to use
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.30,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,to execute our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:24.79,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you also fighting for them, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.59,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You'll save the people sleeping inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:30.50,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Teppei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still hard for you to have fun with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:48.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm the type who prefers \Nto be alone, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:51.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.73,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:58.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone really understands me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:04.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hana is like me, a life form born \Noutside this solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:09.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,However, Hana may have been born like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but her mentality is much \Ncloser to yours than to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:18.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When you become friends with a girl, \Nwhat are you supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have a telepathic kiss like Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:25.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But my experiences and memories are vast
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:30.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and beyond Earth humans' comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:35.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The information shared in a short kiss \Nis only the surface thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:41.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But if I kissed someone deeply, \Nand they touched the other part,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:45.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,who knows what darkness would swallow them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:50.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of thousands, tens of thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:57.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The time I spend with Daichi, \NHana, and you is enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:02.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, in the middle of it, \Nit's as if I return to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:07.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and suddenly it feels like everything \Nis a dream with no substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"What is this I'm looking at?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"Is it truly real, and not just a dream?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:17.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"After thousands, tens of thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:21.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,what is this I find when I meet you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"What am I?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:27.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"Why did I cross this vast gulf of \Ntime and space to come here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"If there is a meaning, what is it?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:38.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I feel as if thoughts \Nlike these are about to crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:47.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean you've finally \Nturned to me for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:57.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I know why you're here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:07.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you're here with me right now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:15.19,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,is that my god crossed vast gulfs of \Nspace and time to lead you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:42.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:47.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,People of the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}, \NI'd like your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:53.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned of the Globe Intercept \NFaction's Operation Summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:59.75,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to stop these ideas \Nthat threaten to destroy humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:03.46,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0} will temporarily \Nremain under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I will now take action to stop Operation Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:11.18,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd like you to know that \Nmy actions are entirely due
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,to my personal desire for all \Nhumanity's continued prosperity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:20.19,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and that I am not part of any \Norganization at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:24.40,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is getting interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:28.86,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... Hirosue, from Salty Dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:38.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking Hana back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:16.68,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Salty Dog's Hirosue has taken over the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:20.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0} is in even more trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.62,0:24:22.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Countless bits of debris in the satellite's orbit
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:25.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,begin to attack the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.65,0:24:28.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This is an attack by the Planetary Gears!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:29.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:31.30,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.30,0:24:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 21 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.82,0:24:36.58,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Meaning of a Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Meaning of a Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, expand!
